data.description: The Dunn and Stone built home is sure to impress the pickiest of buyers! There are 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths & has a 3 car tandem garage. The study & dining room are located off the large entry. This house has a plethora of storage! The living area has soaring ceilings & is open to the kitchen! The nice sized kitchen has upgraded cabinets, stainless steel appliances & granite countertops w/ a large breakfast bar. The butlers pantry boasts beautiful cabinetry w/ granite countertops to match the kitchen and is just off the dining room and kitchen. You will find fresh paint throughout. The primary bedroom is spacious & has it own ensuite w/a soaker tub, separate shower & his & her vanities. Upstairs you will find 3 large bedrooms w/ a massive game room! The back yard is large enough to fit a pool. Albury Trails Estates has a pool & is designated to Klein ISD.
